84191a50-69d5-4720-a87c-e7e42246afb1	https://ideam.ie/smarter-factory-home-page/smarter-factory-landing-page/	Smarter Factory Landing Page | IDEAM	The Smarter Factory Technology Gateway Programme is co-financed by the Government of Ireland and the European Union through the ERDF Southern, Eastern & Midland Regional Programme 2021-2027. 1.Research Projects in the company.. Collaborate with us on tailored research that tackles real challenges in your company. 2.Digital Hub & Researcher access for the company. Gain hands-on access to our digital hub and work directly with experienced researchers. 3.Blend of custom testing, training, certification, validation & upskilling. From testing and certification to training, validation, and staff upskilling, we design solutions around your needs. 4.Masterclasses & Specialist training.. Learn through a blend of broad masterclasses and in-depth specialist training, ensuring your team has the right skills for the future. Jim O’Hagan, Smarter Factory Gateway Manager. TUS Coonagh Engineering Campus Jim O’Hagan, Smarter Factory Gateway Manager. LinkedIn: Smarter Factory Technology Gateway Smarter Factory Core Expertise. The Smarter Factory Technology Gateway, in close collaboration with Enterprise Ireland and industry partners across the manufacturing value chain, focuses on research projects that drive impactful innovation. Smarter Factory Core Expertise. Central to these partnerships is the belief in the power of data. By harnessing cyber-physical systems (CPS), the Internet of Things (IoT), and edge devices, the Gateway enables the development of intelligent systems, cognitive robotics, computer vision, and artificial intelligence (AI). Smarter Factory Core Expertise. Researchers at the University bring deep expertise in areas such as industrial automation, control systems, machine learning, digital twins, algorithm development, and industrial data management. Smarter Factory Core Expertise. A key priority is demonstrating the practical application of these advanced technologies in real industrial settings, helping companies improve product quality, predictive maintenance, efficiency, capacity, cost savings, and sustainability. Smarter Factory Core Expertise. Guided by an Industry Advisory Board and regional stakeholders, the Gateway supports businesses in navigating Industry 4.0 and 5.0, adopting digital manufacturing technologies, and accessing opportunities through national and European research programmes. Smarter Factory Core Expertise. Supporting Operational Excellence and Data-driven Decision making	[-0.070897594,-0.081731275,-0.0037642908,-0.00013206691,0.008480541,-0.0073188986,-0.01698139,-0.0171325,-0.12680028,-0.0388649,0.0124845095,-0.0033564775,0.006591314,-0.025944889,-0.02240281,0.048244048,0.029090237,-0.11161863,0.013954798,-0.13426659,-0.021123154,-0.08499281,-0.022491617,-0.017126162,-0.05765209,-0.016644103,0.051263433,0.010514434,-0.0570036,-0.048823435,-0.010509597,0.033668928,-0.08646201,0.030706586,-0.033725258,0.02297165,0.0039661317,0.048156016,0.11377555,-0.08135714,-0.051414307,-0.11993866,-0.04604561,0.0025412696,0.10223094,0.05244398,-0.018607412,-0.08375321,-0.02916174,-0.0014083219,-0.047370587,-0.08086186,0.03468516,-0.0048097605,-0.01245843,0.049004614,0.10701605,-0.006742914,-0.04688054,0.034175497,0.060531992,-0.067030974,-0.02303454,-0.07784145,-0.011189793,-0.046037696,-0.045810807,0.042110886,-0.05311635,-0.0985377,0.007880126,-0.09030405,-0.08034313,0.08436104,0.03178499,-0.010497771,0.0261765,-0.0139673455,0.13242453,0.010417628,0.04718109,0.14626156,0.00911925,0.0023011798,-0.02086963,-0.0347474,0.0156021835,0.039687127,-0.034401927,0.029882304,0.019433003,-0.043840557,-0.034918476,0.04342476,0.09139644,0.02273185,0.033659715,-0.022371883,0.010532735,-0.029720882,-0.010123942,0.04293631,-0.029922413,-0.046559457,-0.055847727,0.061109066,0.033474527,0.047763053,0.15145622,-0.0024245912,-0.026579916,-0.0052015074,-0.045944944,-0.031008134,-0.06360563,0