1f945d68-80f0-48e8-8b9e-e5fa53bb202c	https://ideam.ie/project/aidea/	AIDEA | IDEAM	AIDEA - Artificial Intelligence for a new Design Education Approach. Short project description: AIDEA aims to increase the quality of European Design Education and its alignment with the market needs by innovating training curricula, strengthening design schools and academies by incorporating the 3 different meanings of “Intelligence”: The Intelligence of the hand, Artificial Intelligence and Social Intelligence. It will do so by enabling teachers to empower students to harness the transformative potential of AI in design while fostering critical thinking, creativity, and ethical awareness.	[-0.057161305,0.06363134,0.0003278875,0.008680524,-0.021426342,-0.027231324,-0.023803305,0.03862704,-0.0030838554,0.04269392,-0.033206623,0.03331532,0.021325547,-0.048915874,-0.08730388,0.066552,0.04240948,-0.050965045,-0.026141852,0.0022381742,0.0011896236,0.015197865,0.058616087,-0.028124524,-0.052614056,0.09276454,0.0885436,-0.065328196,0.008589487,-0.0736263,-0.0021347213,-0.012214461,-0.01918404,-0.02530845,0.05071396,0.07517795,0.019311214,0.034628738,0.022190116,-0.059767496,-0.093273066,-0.07472157,-0.05792687,-0.005490921,0.069491215,0.014185586,-0.10213213,-0.035801284,0.0072304467,-0.01448457,-0.094675325,-0.12549727,-0.049522366,-0.082167506,-0.022613378,0.024034195,-0.0014511684,-0.03975654,-0.03267611,0.047087207,0.069867164,0.015309913,0.035655025,0.02195395,-0.024158424,0.002774667,-0.01491758,0.078233264,-0.05707135,-0.096522704,0.09250907,-0.013661908,0.038129926,-0.0096851,0.09884429,0.06267882,-0.032839164,-0.030155687,0.038252857,-0.07176848,-0.06322969,0.015745291,-0.04134749,0.08287303,0.029174726,-0.033235244,-0.0050946632,-0.03949055,0.07977056,0.0522076,0.03831246,-0.013635235,-0.0006502968,-0.018791588,0.035210878,0.016552482,-0.010635031,-0.068682484,-0.06534918,0.036151562,-0.1305879,0.104286574,-0.0123990765,-0.0147996945,-0.06493798,-0.018534364,0.026437404,-0.0588331