51257bbb-9798-48d9-b35e-939f11c27325	https://ideam.ie/project/skills4circularity/	Skills4Circularity | IDEAM	Skills4Circularity - Upskilling and reskilling the textile industry sector to face the challenges in recycling, traceability and certification of recycled products. Skills4Circularity addresses critical skills shortages in the European textile industry by integrating circular economy principles, digital transformation, and sustainability into vocational and higher education. The project will develop a comprehensive training ecosystem equipping the workforce with future-proof skills through innovative, modular programmes including MOOCs, regional and international bootcamps, and interregional hackathons.	[-0.006500958,0.010808787,-0.04743235,0.004256077,0.04201555,0.0006558469,-0.0051846853,-0.042682838,-0.11234385,-0.053191513,0.010643779,-0.026789285,0.018170197,0.100320466,-0.026341587,0.006552445,-0.05536944,0.039515223,-0.046924595,-0.043153215,-0.0017704795,-0.096226566,0.04156657,-0.007783384,-0.029477946,0.010541947,0.017891902,-0.11870287,-0.01125298,-0.062230937,0.01731138,0.16578552,-0.038564038,0.023549521,0.07347707,0.08041919,0.13581048,0.020852657,0.0234082,-0.012570464,-0.04027871,-0.06986482,-0.060186226,-0.06379749,0.04057057,0.014825099,0.084068015,-0.057691194,-0.014163953,0.014832649,0.021446766,-0.06601043,0.020569758,-0.05393134,-0.04418749,-0.0023635884,0.04020539,0.069865294,-0.034526657,0.051491812,0.075215824,-0.07299789,-0.064209506,0.036699824,0.02554018,0.04127485,-0.06996654,0.040909667,-0.0668598,-0.046977114,0.0035585288,-0.09504688,-0.02744058,0.016375631,0.12975697,0.028978234,-0.009539076,-0.035251364,-0.0073615643,-0.0016475162,0.04088171,0.06548437,-0.0054914234,-0.03192466,-0.063266724,0.011601196,0.006808651,-0.06872776,0.05406371,-0.007211224,0.038234897,-0.024306064,-0.014814731,-0.053907882,-0.010205581,0.039886776,-8.941482e-05,0.056137674,0.03251836,-0.0024788983,-0.082220666,0.0018041036,-0.012691085,-0.003836928,-